DSJobDef.name: DS07_JK_BANK1_And_JK_BANK2_To_COMBINE_CST_INPUT
DSJobDef.longDescription:
Column Mapping between JK Wealth Bank Accounts from Subdevision 1.
This provides a mapping from its JKLW_DBS to the JKLW_ODS.

The Customer data is then standardized and cleansed before it can be integrated into the Enterprise Data Warehouse.This mapping specification looks up detailed Bank Branch  and Customer Demographics and adds these to the collected customer information for BANK 2 LOB.
The customer stage target can then be used as the input for the Custer Master table but to ensure good quality records the target needs to be standardized and cleansed before it can be integrated into JKLW customer master.
